fr.sii.ogham.template.freemarker.adapter

Class FirstSupportingResolverAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.template.freemarker.adapter.FirstSupportingResolverAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TemplateLoaderAdapter

    public class FirstSupportingResolverAdapter
extends Object
implements TemplateLoaderAdapter
    Decorator that will ask each resolver adapter if it is able to handle the template resolver. If the resolver adapter supports it, then this implementation asks the resolver adapter to provide the FreeMarker template loader. Only the first resolver adapter that can handle the template resolver is used.
    Author:
    Cyril Dejonghe
